deleteConfirmation: Are you sure you want to delete?
jaws_play: Click to start and stop the simulation.
jaws_del: Click to delete the actual simulation-settings.
jaws_v: Insert numbers to set the initial speed.
jaws_g: Insert numbers to set the gravity.
jaws_alpha: Insert numbers to set the angle of the cannon.
jaws_h1: Insert numbers to set the height of the cannon.
jaws_d: Insert numbers to set the distance to the target.
jaws_h2: Insert numbers to set the height of the target.
jaws_h1_Slider: Move the slider up or down to change the height of the cannon.
jaws_h2_Slider: Move the slider up or down to change the height of the target.
jaws_d_Slider: Move the slider left or right to change the distance to the target.
jaws_v_Slider: Move the slider to set the initial speed.
jaws_g_Slider: Move the slider to set the gravity.
jaws_grid: Click to switch the grid on and off.
jaws_path: Click to switch the path of the bullet on and off.
jaws_protactor: Click to switch the path of the protraction on and off.
jaws_accessebility: Click to switch the accessebility on and off.
jaws_targetMissed: Oops, you have missed the target
